	author = {Beuschlein, Felix and Fassnacht, Martin and Assié, Guillaume and Calebiro, Davide and Stratakis, Constantine A and Osswald, Andrea and Ronchi, Cristina L and Wieland, Thomas and Sbiera, Silviu and Faucz, Fabio R and Schaak, Katrin and Schmittfull, Anett and Schwarzmayr, Thomas and Barreau, Olivia and Vezzosi, Delphine and Rizk-Rabin, Marthe and Zabel, Ulrike and Szarek, Eva and Salpea, Paraskevi and Forlino, Antonella and Vetro, Annalisa and Zuffardi, Orsetta and Kisker, Caroline and Diener, Susanne and Meitinger, Thomas and Lohse, Martin J and Reincke, Martin and Bertherat, Jérome and Strom, Tim M and Allolio, Bruno},
